# ChunkType Equality operator

Tests two chunk types for equality.

```csharp
public static bool operator ==(ChunkType left, ChunkType right)
```

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| left | The first chunk type. |
| right | The second chunk type. |

## Return Value

Returns `true` if the chunk types are equal; `false` otherwise.
